857
01:05:59.790 --> 01:06:01.500
Oh! Ah...

858
01:06:02.209 --> 01:06:03.377
(sighs)

859
01:06:03.585 --> 01:06:05.337
Oh. fuckin' Jesus.

860
01:06:06.129 --> 01:06:07.589
(gasping)

861
01:06:09.675 --> 01:06:11.093
(creaking)

862
01:06:12.302 --> 01:06:14.054
