Ah...

865
01:06:26.608 --> 01:06:28.318
(rumbling)

866
01:06:48.463 --> 01:06:49.923
(creaking)

867
01:07:17.784 --> 01:07:19.327
(gasping)

868
01:07:26.918 --> 01:07:28.128
