870
01:07:54.529 --> 01:07:56.448
(wind gusting)
(door slamming)

871
01:08:02.704 --> 01:08:04.289
(clanking)

872
01:08:20.472 --> 01:08:22.390
(suspenseful music)

873
01:08:41.326 --> 01:08:42.786
(clock ticking)

874
01:08:43.787 --> 01:08:45.121
(rattling)

875
01:08:50.836 --> 01:08:52.128
(clanking)

876
01:08:57.217 --> 01:08:58.385
