parlour next door as well. yeah.

1191
01:36:22.110 --> 01:36:23.236
Ah.

1192
01:36:23.653 --> 01:36:25.530
Oh. this is from Fergal.

1193
01:36:27.949 --> 01:36:30.118
He's pretty devastated
about Fiona.

1194
01:36:30.368 --> 01:36:32.161
