1204
01:36:57.437 --> 01:37:00.857
Mr Bauman. I need
to tell you something.

1205
01:37:03.652 --> 01:37:06.154
I don't what happened. um.

1206
01:37:06.530 --> 01:37:09.449
but I'm worried it might have
been my fault in some way.

1207
01:37:10.617 --> 01:37:11.743
How?

1208
