There was a flask of whiskey
in your room.

1209
01:37:16.331 --> 01:37:18.667
- Did you drink it?
- Yeah.

1210
01:37:19.167 --> 01:37:20.460
Much of it?

1211
01:37:20.835 --> 01:37:23.588
Well. it's whiskey.
I drink all of it. Why?

1212
01:37:25.215 --> 01:37:26.716
I spiked it.

1213
01:37:28.134 --> 01:37:29.636
